dc.title: Congressman Jerry McNerney : Representing California's 11th District
dc.description: Congressman Jerry McNerney represents California in the U.S. House of Representatives. He is proud to serve in the U.S. House of Representatives representing California's 11th District, which includes parts of San Joaquin County in the Central Valley as well as parts of Contra Costa, Alameda and Santa Clara Counties in the Bay Area.
